<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= pageTitle %> - AttendanceMS</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root { --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); }
    body { background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    .help-header { background: var(--primary-gradient); color: white; padding: 3rem 0 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .privacy-section { background: white; border-radius: 15px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .back-nav { position: fixed; top: 2rem; right: 2rem; z-index: 1000; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .back-nav { position: relative; top: auto; right: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="back-nav">
    <a href="/help" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Help</a>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt me-2"></i>Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <div class="help-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-3"></i>Privacy & Data Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">How we protect and handle your data</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="privacy-section">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-database me-2"></i>Data We Collect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Student Information:</strong> Names, roll numbers, attendance records</li>
        <li><strong>Teacher Information:</strong> Names, email addresses, phone numbers</li>
        <li><strong>Parent Information:</strong> Email addresses, phone numbers for notifications</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Login times, feature usage for system improvement</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-users me-2"></i>Who Can Access Data</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Teachers:</strong> Can access their own classes and students only</li>
        <li><strong>Administrators:</strong> Can access school-wide data for management purposes</li>
        <li><strong>Parents:</strong> Can only view their own child's attendance data</li>
        <li><strong>Support Staff:</strong> Limited access for technical support only</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-clock me-2"></i>Data Retention</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Attendance records: Retained for 7 years as per educational standards</li>
        <li>User accounts: Active as long as user is associated with the institution</li>
        <li>Logs and analytics: Retained for 2 years for system improvement</li>
        <li>Deleted data: Permanently removed within 30 days of deletion request</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-lock me-2"></i>Data Security</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>All data encrypted in transit and at rest</li>
        <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
        <li>Access controls and user authentication</li>
        <li>Regular backups stored securely</li>
        <li>Compliance with educational data privacy standards</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-section">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-user-check me-2"></i>Your Rights</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update incorrect information</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your data</li>
        <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Export your data in standard formats</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Contact <a href="/help/contact">support</a> to exercise these rights.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>